				<td colspan="2"><span>Not a huge raid, but definately a big save...
<br />

<br />
Got to the last named on Tipt.  Pulled the dude, and soon the first tank goes down.  The wizzy goes down.  next dude goes down.  Cleric goes down.  I now have solid aggro... he hits me one round, deftdance.  I tank him for the whole time of deftdance and just as it finishes, I fade.  The last person there was an underpowered pally we were trying to get the flag.  He gets aggro until he dies... and then the dude turns back on me.  My DS killed him as he killed me.  (not even any xp loss =O.  and I got 8pct AA xp for the kill =O)
<br />

<br />
we ran back, I ran up nekkid, /corpsed my body thru the gate, looted, drug the bodies to just right by the hail mob.  Ran up a cleric, who rezzed the pally b4 dying.  Pally accepted rez, rezzed the rest of the group, all hailed, and we got 4 new tipt flags...
<br />

<br />
Deftdance (as well as everything else we tried) saved us 3+ hours worth of work probably.
<br />

<br />
Keldridge</span></td>
